2025-07-02 01:43:27.587 +05:30 [INF] Executed DbCommand (46ms) [Parameters=[@__userId_0='?' (DbType = Guid)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p."Id", p."Content", p."IsDeleted", p."PostStatus", p."Title", p."UserId", u."Id", u."CreatedAt", u."Email", u."IsDeleted", u."IsSuspended", u."Name", u."PasswordHash", u."Role", u."Status", u."SuspendedUntil", u."SuspensionReason", i0."Id", i0."Content", i0."IsDeleted", i0."Name", i0."PostId", i0."UploadedAt", c1."Id", c1."Content", c1."CreatedAt", c1."IsDeleted", c1."PostId", c1."Status", c1."UserId", l."Id", l."IsLiked", l."PostId", l."UserId"
FROM "Posts" AS p
INNER JOIN "Users" AS u ON p."UserId" = u."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT i."Id", i."Content", i."IsDeleted", i."Name", i."PostId", i."UploadedAt"
    FROM "Images" AS i
    WHERE NOT (i."IsDeleted")
) AS i0 ON p."Id" = i0."PostId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT c0."Id", c0."Content", c0."CreatedAt", c0."IsDeleted", c0."PostId", c0."Status", c0."UserId"
    FROM "Comments" AS c0
    WHERE NOT (c0."IsDeleted")
) AS c1 ON p."Id" = c1."PostId"
LEFT JOIN "Likes" AS l ON p."Id" = l."PostId"
WHERE NOT (p."IsDeleted") AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "Comments" AS c
    WHERE p."Id" = c."PostId" AND c."UserId" = @__userId_0 AND NOT (c."IsDeleted"))
ORDER BY p."Id", u."Id", i0."Id", c1."Id"

FROM "Posts" AS p
INNER JOIN "Users" AS u ON p."UserId" = u."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT i."Id", i."Content", i."IsDeleted", i."Name", i."PostId", i."UploadedAt"
    FROM "Images" AS i
    WHERE NOT (i."IsDeleted")
) AS i0 ON p."Id" = i0."PostId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT c0."Id", c0."Content", c0."CreatedAt", c0."IsDeleted", c0."PostId", c0."Status", c0."UserId"
    FROM "Comments" AS c0
    WHERE NOT (c0."IsDeleted")
) AS c1 ON p."Id" = c1."PostId"
LEFT JOIN "Likes" AS l ON p."Id" = l."PostId"
WHERE NOT (p."IsDeleted") AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "Comments" AS c
    WHERE p."Id" = c."PostId" AND c."UserId" = @__userId_0 AND NOT (c."IsDeleted"))
ORDER BY p."Id", u."Id", i0."Id", c1."Id"

2025-07-02 02:16:07.213 +05:30 [INF] Executed DbCommand (38ms) [Parameters=[@__userId_0='?' (DbType = Guid)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p."Id", p."Content", p."IsDeleted", p."PostStatus", p."Title", p."UserId", u."Id", u."CreatedAt", u."Email", u."IsDeleted", u."IsSuspended", u."Name", u."PasswordHash", u."Role", u."Status", u."SuspendedUntil", u."SuspensionReason", i0."Id", i0."Content", i0."IsDeleted", i0."Name", i0."PostId", i0."UploadedAt", c0."Id", c0."Content", c0."CreatedAt", c0."IsDeleted", c0."PostId", c0."Status", c0."UserId", l."Id", l."IsLiked", l."PostId", l."UserId"
FROM "Posts" AS p
INNER JOIN "Users" AS u ON p."UserId" = u."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT i."Id", i."Content", i."IsDeleted", i."Name", i."PostId", i."UploadedAt"
    FROM "Images" AS i
    WHERE NOT (i."IsDeleted")
) AS i0 ON p."Id" = i0."PostId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT c."Id", c."Content", c."CreatedAt", c."IsDeleted", c."PostId", c."Status", c."UserId"
    FROM "Comments" AS c
    WHERE NOT (c."IsDeleted")
) AS c0 ON p."Id" = c0."PostId"
LEFT JOIN "Likes" AS l ON p."Id" = l."PostId"
WHERE p."UserId" = @__userId_0 AND NOT (p."IsDeleted")
ORDER BY p."Id", u."Id", i0."Id", c0."Id"

SELECT p."Id", p."Content", p."IsDeleted", p."PostStatus", p."Title", p."UserId", u."Id", u."CreatedAt", u."Email", u."IsDeleted", u."IsSuspended", u."Name", u."PasswordHash", u."Role", u."Status", u."SuspendedUntil", u."SuspensionReason", i0."Id", i0."Content", i0."IsDeleted", i0."Name", i0."PostId", i0."UploadedAt", c1."Id", c1."Content", c1."CreatedAt", c1."IsDeleted", c1."PostId", c1."Status", c1."UserId", l."Id", l."IsLiked", l."PostId", l."UserId"
FROM "Posts" AS p
INNER JOIN "Users" AS u ON p."UserId" = u."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT i."Id", i."Content", i."IsDeleted", i."Name", i."PostId", i."UploadedAt"
    FROM "Images" AS i
    WHERE NOT (i."IsDeleted")
) AS i0 ON p."Id" = i0."PostId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT c0."Id", c0."Content", c0."CreatedAt", c0."IsDeleted", c0."PostId", c0."Status", c0."UserId"
    FROM "Comments" AS c0
    WHERE NOT (c0."IsDeleted")
) AS c1 ON p."Id" = c1."PostId"
LEFT JOIN "Likes" AS l ON p."Id" = l."PostId"
WHERE NOT (p."IsDeleted") AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "Comments" AS c
    WHERE p."Id" = c."PostId" AND c."UserId" = @__userId_0 AND NOT (c."IsDeleted"))
ORDER BY p."Id", u."Id", i0."Id", c1."Id"

    SELECT i."Id", i."Content", i."IsDeleted", i."Name", i."PostId", i."UploadedAt"
    FROM "Images" AS i

SELECT p."Id", p."Content", p."IsDeleted", p."PostStatus", p."Title", p."UserId", u."Id", u."CreatedAt", u."Email", u."IsDeleted", u."IsSuspended", u."Name", u."PasswordHash", u."Role", u."Status", u."SuspendedUntil", u."SuspensionReason", i0."Id", i0."Content", i0."IsDeleted", i0."Name", i0."PostId", i0."UploadedAt", c1."Id", c1."Content", c1."CreatedAt", c1."IsDeleted", c1."PostId", c1."Status", c1."UserId", l."Id", l."IsLiked", l."PostId", l."UserId"
FROM "Posts" AS p
INNER JOIN "Users" AS u ON p."UserId" = u."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT i."Id", i."Content", i."IsDeleted", i."Name", i."PostId", i."UploadedAt"
    FROM "Images" AS i
    WHERE NOT (i."IsDeleted")
) AS i0 ON p."Id" = i0."PostId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT c0."Id", c0."Content", c0."CreatedAt", c0."IsDeleted", c0."PostId", c0."Status", c0."UserId"
    FROM "Comments" AS c0
    WHERE NOT (c0."IsDeleted")
) AS c1 ON p."Id" = c1."PostId"
LEFT JOIN "Likes" AS l ON p."Id" = l."PostId"
WHERE NOT (p."IsDeleted") AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "Comments" AS c
    WHERE p."Id" = c."PostId" AND c."UserId" = @__userId_0 AND NOT (c."IsDeleted"))
ORDER BY p."Id", u."Id", i0."Id", c1."Id"

    SELECT c0."Id", c0."Content", c0."CreatedAt", c0."IsDeleted", c0."PostId", c0."Status", c0."UserId"

) AS c1 ON p."Id" = c1."PostId"

FROM "Posts" AS p
INNER JOIN "Users" AS u ON p."UserId" = u."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT i."Id", i."Content", i."IsDeleted", i."Name", i."PostId", i."UploadedAt"
    FROM "Images" AS i
    WHERE NOT (i."IsDeleted")
) AS i0 ON p."Id" = i0."PostId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT c0."Id", c0."Content", c0."CreatedAt", c0."IsDeleted", c0."PostId", c0."Status", c0."UserId"
    FROM "Comments" AS c0
    WHERE NOT (c0."IsDeleted")
) AS c1 ON p."Id" = c1."PostId"
LEFT JOIN "Likes" AS l ON p."Id" = l."PostId"
WHERE NOT (p."IsDeleted") AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "Comments" AS c
    WHERE p."Id" = c."PostId" AND c."UserId" = @__userId_0 AND NOT (c."IsDeleted"))
ORDER BY p."Id", u."Id", i0."Id", c1."Id"

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT i."Id", i."Content", i."IsDeleted", i."Name", i."PostId", i."UploadedAt"
    FROM "Images" AS i
    WHERE NOT (i."IsDeleted")
) AS i0 ON p."Id" = i0."PostId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT c0."Id", c0."Content", c0."CreatedAt", c0."IsDeleted", c0."PostId", c0."Status", c0."UserId"
    FROM "Comments" AS c0
    WHERE NOT (c0."IsDeleted")
) AS c1 ON p."Id" = c1."PostId"
LEFT JOIN "Likes" AS l ON p."Id" = l."PostId"
WHERE NOT (p."IsDeleted") AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "Comments" AS c
    WHERE p."Id" = c."PostId" AND c."UserId" = @__userId_0 AND NOT (c."IsDeleted"))

    SELECT c0."Id", c0."Content", c0."CreatedAt", c0."IsDeleted", c0."PostId", c0."Status", c0."UserId"

    WHERE NOT (c0."IsDeleted")
) AS c1 ON p."Id" = c1."PostId"

2025-07-02 02:43:07.412 +05:30 [INF] Executed DbCommand (4ms) [Parameters=[@__userId_0='?' (DbType = Guid)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p."Id", p."Content", p."IsDeleted", p."PostStatus", p."Title", p."UserId", u."Id", u."CreatedAt", u."Email", u."IsDeleted", u."IsSuspended", u."Name", u."PasswordHash", u."Role", u."Status", u."SuspendedUntil", u."SuspensionReason", i0."Id", i0."Content", i0."IsDeleted", i0."Name", i0."PostId", i0."UploadedAt", c1."Id", c1."Content", c1."CreatedAt", c1."IsDeleted", c1."PostId", c1."Status", c1."UserId", l."Id", l."IsLiked", l."PostId", l."UserId"
FROM "Posts" AS p
INNER JOIN "Users" AS u ON p."UserId" = u."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT i."Id", i."Content", i."IsDeleted", i."Name", i."PostId", i."UploadedAt"
    FROM "Images" AS i
    WHERE NOT (i."IsDeleted")
) AS i0 ON p."Id" = i0."PostId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT c0."Id", c0."Content", c0."CreatedAt", c0."IsDeleted", c0."PostId", c0."Status", c0."UserId"
    FROM "Comments" AS c0
    WHERE NOT (c0."IsDeleted")
) AS c1 ON p."Id" = c1."PostId"
LEFT JOIN "Likes" AS l ON p."Id" = l."PostId"
WHERE NOT (p."IsDeleted") AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "Comments" AS c
    WHERE p."Id" = c."PostId" AND c."UserId" = @__userId_0 AND NOT (c."IsDeleted"))
ORDER BY p."Id", u."Id", i0."Id", c1."Id"

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT c0."Id", c0."Content", c0."CreatedAt", c0."IsDeleted", c0."PostId", c0."Status", c0."UserId"

    WHERE NOT (c0."IsDeleted")
) AS c1 ON p."Id" = c1."PostId"

    FROM "Comments" AS c

FROM "Posts" AS p
INNER JOIN "Users" AS u ON p."UserId" = u."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT i."Id", i."Content", i."IsDeleted", i."Name", i."PostId", i."UploadedAt"
    FROM "Images" AS i
    WHERE NOT (i."IsDeleted")
) AS i0 ON p."Id" = i0."PostId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT c0."Id", c0."Content", c0."CreatedAt", c0."IsDeleted", c0."PostId", c0."Status", c0."UserId"
    FROM "Comments" AS c0
    WHERE NOT (c0."IsDeleted")
) AS c1 ON p."Id" = c1."PostId"
LEFT JOIN "Likes" AS l ON p."Id" = l."PostId"
WHERE NOT (p."IsDeleted") AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "Comments" AS c
    WHERE p."Id" = c."PostId" AND c."UserId" = @__userId_0 AND NOT (c."IsDeleted"))
ORDER BY p."Id", u."Id", i0."Id", c1."Id"

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT i."Id", i."Content", i."IsDeleted", i."Name", i."PostId", i."UploadedAt"
    FROM "Images" AS i
    WHERE NOT (i."IsDeleted")
) AS i0 ON p."Id" = i0."PostId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT c0."Id", c0."Content", c0."CreatedAt", c0."IsDeleted", c0."PostId", c0."Status", c0."UserId"
    FROM "Comments" AS c0
    WHERE NOT (c0."IsDeleted")
) AS c1 ON p."Id" = c1."PostId"
